# `dist/index.html` is intentionally checked in — `crates/note_item`
# embeds it via `include_str!()` and Cargo builds must not require
# a JS toolchain.  Rebuild with `pnpm build` after editor changes.
# Negates the root `.gitignore`'s `dist` rule so future commits don't
# need `git add -f`.
!dist/
!dist/index.html
